<section class="sec" id="process">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <div class="num">§ 01</div>
      <div class="title">
        <div class="eye">Process</div>
        <h2 class="display">Piping data in.<br />Routed circuits out.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="desc">No CAD plugin. No onboarding. You email the brief; the engineering team returns a solved result.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="how-line">
      <div class="s">
        <div class="n"><span>01 · Brief</span><span>≤ 1 day</span></div>
        <div class="t">You&nbsp;send</div>
        <div class="d">PCF / Isogen export + tracing brief: heating mode, tracer type, temperature profile.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="s">
        <div class="n"><span>02 · Model</span><span>Graph</span></div>
        <div class="t">We&nbsp;model</div>
        <div class="d">Piping parsed into a weighted graph. Bridge candidates generated. No manual data cleanup.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="s">
        <div class="n"><span>03 · Optimize</span><span>RPS + ALNS</span></div>
        <div class="t">We&nbsp;solve</div>
        <div class="d">Two-stage solver — Reactive Path-Scanning then Adaptive Large Neighborhood Search. Deterministic.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="s">
        <div class="n"><span>04 · Deliver</span><span>XYZ · BOM</span></div>
        <div class="t">You&nbsp;receive</div>
        <div class="d"><b>(x, y, z)</b> polylines, per-circuit BOM, constraint verification, side-by-side vs your manual baseline.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="clip-slot">
      <div class="inner">
        <div>
          <div class="pill">● PROCESS CLIP · COMING SOON</div>
          <div class="ti">From brief to circuits</div>
          <div class="sub">Short video · ~20s · loop</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="play">
        <span>00:00</span>
        <div class="bar"></div>
        <span>00:20</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
